# Network Commands

Useful network-related commands for diagnostics and scanning.

---

## üîç Network Info

```bash
ip a                 # Show network interfaces and IP addresses
ifconfig             # Display network configuration (older tool)
ping HOST            # Check connectivity
traceroute HOST      # Display the route to a host
netstat -tuln        # Show listening ports and services
